Venglustat, an orally administered glucosylceramide synthase inhibitor: 
Assessment over 3 years in adult males with classic Fabry disease in an 
open-label phase 2 study and its extension study.

Deegan PB(1), Goker-Alpan O(2), Geberhiwot T(3), Hopkin RJ(4), Lukina E(5), 
Tylki-Szymanska A(6), Zaher A(7), Sensinger C(8), Gaemers SJM(9), Modur V(10), 
